OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775268200
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show garden to 'inspire
OL,4,Ccuriosity' gets royal seal of approval
OL,6,FThe design for a garden at the Chelsea
OL,7,FFlower Show to encourage people's
OL,8,Fcuriosity towards gardening and nature
OL,9,Fhas been given a royal seal of
OL,10,Fapproval.
OL,12,FThe King was joined at his Highgrove
OL,13,Fresidence in Gloucestershire by Sir
OL,14,FDavid Beckham, Alan Titchmarsh and
OL,15,Fgarden designer Frances Tophill to put
OL,16,Fthe finishing touches on the Royal
OL,17,FHorticultural Society (RHS) and King's
OL,18,FFoundation Curious Garden which will
OL,19,Ffeature at the world famous show.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
