FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775268200
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show garden to 'inspire
OL,4,Ccuriosity' gets royal seal of approval
OL,6,FThe display has been designed by Ms
OL,7,FTophill and is being championed by
OL,8,FCharles, King's Foundation ambassador
OL,9,FSir David and leading horticulturalist
OL,10,Fand TV gardener Titchmarsh ` an RHS
OL,11,Fand King's Foundation ambassador ` who
OL,12,Fhave all had input into the garden's
OL,13,Fdesign.
OL,15,FAt the meeting at Highgrove it was
OL,16,Fagreed the garden will feature a
OL,17,Fbeehive, inspired by the King and Sir
OL,18,FDavid's enthusiasm for beekeeping and
OL,19,Fproducing honey.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775268200
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show garden to 'inspire
OL,4,Ccuriosity' gets royal seal of approval
OL,6,FThe beehive will go in the garden,
OL,7,Fwhich will be free of man-made
OL,8,Fmaterials, alongside previously-
OL,9,Fannounced features including an oak
OL,10,Fbuilding that represents a "museum of
OL,11,Fcuriosities", and seven raised beds in
OL,12,Fa nod to Sir David's famous number 7
OL,13,Fshirt in the Manchester United and
OL,14,FEngland teams.
OL,16,FThe garden will also feature
OL,17,Fdelphiniums, one of the King's
OL,18,Ffavourite flowers, and roses named
OL,19,Fafter the three champions.
OL,26,@rD@\OUsD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
