OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show garden to 'inspire
OL,4,Ccuriosity' gets royal seal of approval
OL,6,FIn video footage, Sir David is heard
OL,7,Fchatting to the King about the "very
OL,8,Fspecial" Sir David Beckham rose, which
OL,9,Fhis teenager daughter Harper had named
OL,10,Fafter him for his 50th birthday.
OL,12,FThe King asks about the bloom as they
OL,13,Fsit around a table to discuss the
OL,14,Fdesigns, saying: "What colour is that?"
OL,16,FSir David tells him: "White. My
OL,17,Fdaughter actually, it was a gift from
OL,18,Fher for my 50th birthday last year....
OL,26,@oD@`OUpD@HO]vD@ROUvD@gO]xD@VOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
