SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775268200
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show garden to 'inspire
OL,4,Ccuriosity' gets royal seal of approval
OL,6,FThe presenter tells the monarch,
OL,7,Fprompting more laughter, that it's
OL,8,F"pink with a sort of peony-shaped
OL,9,Fflower, but apparently I have a
OL,10,Fslightly weak neck, but if you prune
OL,11,Fme hard, I'm quite... It's true
OL,12,Factually, yeah really."
OL,14,FThere could even be a gnome or two in
OL,15,Fthe garden ` as the RHS lifts its
OL,16,FChelsea show ban on the ornamental
OL,17,Ffigures for only the second time in
OL,18,Fhistory ` celebrating a tradition at
OL,19,FHighgrove where a gnome is often to be
OL,20,Ffound in the stumpery.
OL,26,@pD@AOUtD@WO]
