PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775268200
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show garden to 'inspire
OL,4,Ccuriosity' gets royal seal of approval
OL,6,FGnomes decorated by celebrities will
OL,7,Fbe on display at this year's Chelsea,
OL,8,Fand will be auctioned off to raise
OL,9,Ffunds for the RHS's campaign for
OL,10,Fschool gardening.
OL,12,FSir David said afterwards it was "fun"
OL,13,Fto be working on the curious garden
OL,14,Fand he was "excited" for people to see
OL,15,Fit at Chelsea.
OL,17,F"Both The King's Foundation and the
OL,18,FRHS do such great work in protecting
OL,19,Fand promoting green spaces across the
OL,20,FUK," he said.
OL,26,@tD@bOUtD@fO]vD@LOUvD@TO]yD@AOU|D@DO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
