OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775268200
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show garden to 'inspire
OL,4,Ccuriosity' gets royal seal of approval
OL,6,FGarden trainees and apprentices from
OL,7,Fboth RHS Wisley gardens and Highgrove
OL,8,FGardens have been involved in the
OL,9,Fproject and will help with
OL,10,Fconstructing the garden onsite at the
OL,11,FRoyal Hospital Chelsea, and the King
OL,12,Fheard from trainees about their
OL,13,Finvolvement as part of the meeting.
OL,15,FMs Tophill said she "can't wait" to
OL,16,Fshare the curious garden.
OL,18,F"As my first Chelsea garden for the
OL,19,FRHS, I am thrilled to be working on
OL,20,Fsuch a special design.
OL,26,@wD@UOUwD@`O]zD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
