OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1775268200
OL,3,CChelsea Flower Show garden to 'inspire
OL,4,Ccuriosity' gets royal seal of approval
OL,6,F"It has been inspiring to spend time
OL,7,Fat Highgrove and learn more about His
OL,8,FMajesty's approach to gardening and
OL,9,Fhow he incorporates his Harmony
OL,10,Fphilosophy into all of the work that
OL,11,Ftakes place there ` which we have
OL,12,Fbrought to the designs for the
OL,13,Fgarden," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@HO]
